                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "stepNo":  "3",
                    "stepDescription": "Add all dry spices, cook for a minute. Now add tomato puree and salt and fry till oil starts separating. Add water, once it  comes to boil, add boiled eggs. Reduce the flame to low and simmer for 5 mins. Garnish with coriander leaves",
